com.communote.server.web.commons.i18n

Interface JsMessagesExtension

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContentTypeExtractorJsMessages, CustomJsMessages, EmbedJsMessages, HtmlClientJsMessages

    public interface JsMessagesExtension
    Extension to add additional message keys to categories managed by the JsMessagesRegistry.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Map<String,Set<String>> getJsMessageKeys()
      Returns the message keys to add to the named category.

    • Method Detail

      • getJsMessageKeys

        Map<String,Set<String>> getJsMessageKeys()
        Returns the message keys to add to the named category. When creating a Javascript object with message key to localized message mappings for that category the returned message keys will be included.
        Returns:
        a mapping of category name to message key collection. If the category name is not yet known a new category will be created, otherwise the existing one will be extended.
